    <div class="well">
       <p style="font-size:18px;text-align:center;"><strong>Recommendations:</strong><br>
       -  Trekking poles were absolutely crucial. <br>
       -  Make sure your boots fit properly and are worn in. <br>
       -  Salami is a perfect for the trail. <br>
       -  Bring an apple per person for the first day. <br>
       - Don't keep anything that melts inside your "brain", or top of your pack.
